# Marque repository CODEOWNERS
#
# Listed users/teams are automatically requested for review when a PR touches
# the matching paths. CODEOWNERS is advisory — merge rules live in
# GOVERNANCE.md, not here.

# Spec text — full editor team
/spec/            @marque-protocol/editors
/drafts/          @marque-protocol/editors

# MIPs — full editor team (no single editor can self-approve)
/mips/            @marque-protocol/editors

# Governance / process — editor-in-chief plus full team
/GOVERNANCE.md    @marque-protocol/editors
/CONTRIBUTING.md  @marque-protocol/editors
/SECURITY.md      @marque-protocol/editors

# Schemas and examples — editors plus schema-wg sub-team
/schemas/         @marque-protocol/editors @marque-protocol/schema-wg
/examples/        @marque-protocol/editors @marque-protocol/schema-wg

# CI config
/.github/         @marque-protocol/editors

# Docs — anyone on the editors team can review
/docs/            @marque-protocol/editors
